      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c39da999e9109a1b3ca69ef"
      },
      "index": 0,
      "text": "\"To all civilian traffic, this is the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTDF],TDF]] DropShip <i>Armenia</i> currently coordinating relief efforts to [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSebha],Sebha]]. You are hereby warned that several areas of the planet are currently under quarantine to contain local disease outbreaks. \n\nAll traffic should use designated landing pads and follow all safety rules and procedures. This is a recording, use emergency channels if required to report any incidents.\"",
