    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ceb63df6835f757cdfa5ceb"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The message continues with a long list of safety procedures for JumpShip and DropShip crews while in this system. \n\nI've been talking to other captains, and they're not worried about a possible blockade. The Taurians do not have enough naval resources in the system to pull it off and they're more concerned about the outbreaks, which seem to be spreading faster than usual for the season.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cf3c3dda06f88446e34ec1e"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3a06230355c18000067",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c72ac412d745f6704e538f8"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeripheryPox],Periphery Pox]] epidemics can be bad in the most virulent cases, but as long as we limit our time on the planet we should be fine.\n\nWhat I'm more concerned with is this new contract, especially considering our recent interactions with the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreEvilEye],Evil Eye]]. I can't say that I'm happy with the way things turned out.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Neither am I, Doctor, but there was no easy way out.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cd1ca8ec115b309b822526d"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cec7cc0764f0032f01031be"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Getting back to the matter at hand, the contract is straight forward. \n\nThe Eye discovered the origin of the stealth BattleMech that Professor Bambo recovered on Johnson's Reef from the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAntithesisCreed],Creed]]. Since it's too guarded for direct assault, one of our MechWarriors will join an Eye team in infiltrating this cache. Once they're inside and have secured the Mech Bay, they'll board and override the safety procedures of the BattleMechs located there and use them to defend the facility until reinforcements arrive.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c42aed80d07bb6257d7da4b"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": {
        "ops": [
          {
            "functionName": "Play BattleTech Audio Event",
            "args": [
              {
                "int_value": 0,
                "bool_value": false,
                "float_value": 0.0,
                "string_value": "GConv-BeginMusic-GC_111_RENT_TO_OWN",
                "call_value": null,
                "variableref_value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "comment": "GConv-BeginMusic-GC_111_RENT_TO_OWN"
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c8e5c530d337608ef3c27fe"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Assuming that we trust the Eye's intel. Have they shown any proof that there's one of those stealth 'Mechs inside? Otherwise, we might end up with whatever the Creed might be storing down there, instead of what they promised us.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c8a762e964216fa3f35c167"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f36230355c1800006a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c8bf27eac3fb5445d474ca4"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "They have provided no additional information, but quite frankly they have a lot more to risk than us and all of their MechWarriors are inexperienced, so they need our leadership to survive the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInheritors],Inheritor]] counter-attack.\n\nPlus, we performed their request, so if there's anything such as thief honor, they'll be obliged to ensure that the deal was honest.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cc28fe08ded40161d3efd8e"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "But otherwise, that leaves us with one of our MechWarriors in the hands of the Evil Eye, in case they betray us. That whole experience while en route here just made me more uneasy about the whole situation. \n\nI won't ever really trust them, no matter how things play out, because I don't like their methods.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cd586ebbec24cfc2cbe5520"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ce601589b08b8ba5869dc52"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "I second that. While the Eye helped us identify one major security flaw in the interest of this operation, we could be risking the life of one of our MechWarriors. \n\nAnd just because we got one mole, doesn't mean that we got all of them. This whole operation could be blown and instead of infantry guards, the infiltration team might run into an full ambush.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 8,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cc6aed9902e47c7108411e8"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f36230355c1800006a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c44bde561e0aaec28edd087"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Well, the alternative would be to propose to the Eye that we assault the cache ourselves. It might be a nut too tough to crack for us.\n\nWhat do you think, {COMMANDER.FirstName}?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "<color=#85DBF6FF>[Story Decision: Assign a MechWarrior to the Eye's team.]</color> We will show proper leadership to the Eye's MechWarriors.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 9,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c286cbe28872f3677bfc08c"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        },
        {
          "responseText": "<color=#85DBF6FF>[Story Decision: Propose instead to directly assault the cache with your unit.]</color> We can't rely on inexperienced MechWarriors to hold out against an assault. We'll do this ourselves and share the spoils with the Eye.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 11,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c5e4324d57e267cc83e14c7"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c62ffc0acffc9830b5a0b8f"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "I wouldn't surprised if you volunteer yourself to the mission, {COMMANDER.FirstName}. I'll contact the Eye and tell them that we're ready for the operation. ",
